Jihosoft WhatsMate 1.3.6 - SeuPirate

Jihosoft WhatsMate is an all-in-one program that helps you manage WhatsApp data on both your Android and iOS device. With this WhatsApp manager, you will find it super easy and convenient to backup and restore WhatsApp data, transfer WhatsApp files, and even recover deleted WhatsApp data without backup. Surely you will get an excellent experience with this tool and you won’t miss it.

Powerful WhatsApp Manager for Android & iOS
Your complete solution to backup, restore, and transfer WhatsApp data
Backup & restore WhatsApp chats on Android & iOS devices
Transfer WhatsApp data between Android & iPhone
Recover deleted WhatsApp messages without backup
Support Samsung, iPhone, HTC, LG, Sony, Motorola, etc
Fast & stable, safe & efficient, user-friendly
